Time":"2017-05-22T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔該晒刺身前輩嘅回答，我想問吓今年咁多蚊關唔關今年嘅天氣事？</blockquote><br />\n應該就唔關事<br />\n蚊既滋生同積水有關，但偏偏今年暫時雨量偏少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcde71c863f96b9cd45240f8f5c10397d9617874","tid":251212,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係喎請問咁多位前輩點解三月至五月呢段時間咁多雲，我記得上年唔係咁個喎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五月多雲係正常既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年五月雲量特別多可能就係<br />\n因為落唔出雨，雲日日積係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三至四月都係冷暖交替既時間，<br />\n少陽光係正常，不過一般呢兩個月<br />\n應該係好大霧，今年接近無咁既日子，<br />\n可能係冷空氣一直偏弱造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時先出返太陽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n6月上旬末<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過要預一見返多d太陽就會係<br />\n香港聞名於世既濕熱28-33<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就想遲多少少先入呢個階段，<br />\n畢竟之後唔計中間會有打風同其他系統<br />\n既暴雨，濕熱起碼持續到10月頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夏天遲左遠至少都希望佢遲少少開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時最低溫29度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc0b86d824c8fdd2b386d55f1ac706125e0159b","tid":251212,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T16:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔該晒刺身前輩嘅回答，我想問吓今年咁多蚊關唔關今年嘅天氣事？</blockquote><br />\n應該就唔關事<br />\n蚊既滋生同積水有關，但偏偏今年暫時雨量偏少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n氣溫都有少少影響既，今年冬季偏暖，4月有幾日已經26，27度夜溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而呢幾日涼左就少左蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd426e16b547904404136fa6d155d44fa40a0eb3","tid":251212,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"種清涼體感今晚終於無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細風兼潮濕好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b77b1e4549967a40ca776a840b58da98a7da3c","tid":251212,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>種清涼體感今晚終於無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細風兼潮濕好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有喎"},{"pid":"bfced5e78a68f8b79dee8a81071e3f0db68390e1","tid":251212,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>種清涼體感今晚終於無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細風兼潮濕好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日日落已經feel到開始焗，<br />\n同下午果陣涼爽明顯唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3528d70094ce89a5c89a257fcd9b6ffa4df31960","tid":251212,"uid":37210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623feb7bf90cbc8df9a7c9229f274bf1705251ac","tid":251212,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:38:53.000Z","msg":"突然之間好大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7221ebe9f36cfa8ba8c28f9052a79ed50a8673","tid":251212,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:43:38.000Z","msg":"黃雨"},{"pid":"781dc6471dfeee5c2454c733035d4ce1a85a3863","tid":251212,"uid":13614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:46:36.000Z","msg":"開身返工濕撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1762a33f55fc7dcb53ca29fe1ab3b1b09967a8","tid":251212,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:50:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大雨警報</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>請在以下帖文集中討論大雨：</ins></span></span><br />\n【大雨警報】與低壓槽相關的雷雨區影響本港（2017/5/24）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/255319\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/255319</a></strong>"},{"pid":"0629dfe31d5f01a7bef9f186cc629ebce9f630f2","tid":251212,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T22:51:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大雨警報</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>請在以下帖文集中討論大雨：</ins></span></span><br />\n【大雨警報】與低壓槽相關的雷雨區正影響本港（2017/5/24）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/255319\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/255319</a></strong>"},{"pid":"ee642df4a4622683e33f180da207e9bcb8b7daaa","tid":251212,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T05:40:21.000Z","msg":"出面成堆都係咁嘅logic:<